5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Belmont"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Belmont? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Belmont, Carindale, Tingalpa and Gumdale. Our 5-star instructors help Belmont students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Belmont is an intriguing transitional suburb in the east. It features exceptionally quiet, undulating residential pockets completely insulated from the massive, aggressive arterial borders of the Gateway Motorway and Old Cleveland Road. This creates an ideal, self-contained training ground."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"Our instructors use the silent, hilly loops inside Belmont to teach quiet braking control and low-speed maneuvers. Once these are perfected, the student is pushed out onto the high-speed ramps of the Gateway or the commercial density of Old Cleveland Road. This intense juxtaposition prepares a Belmont learner smoothly for the Greenslopes TMR test."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Belmont learners typically test at the Greenslopes TMR Customer Service Centre. Free pickup from Belmont, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5","children":"📍"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-gray-900 block mb-1","children":"Old Cleveland Road"}],["$","span",nu